item.title: About
item.description: Hi, I’m Daniel! I am a Computer Science student at Rochester Institute of Technology. In my free time, I enjoy exercise, video games, and problem solving. I’m always open to learning new technologies and improving my critical thinking skills. I’m still learning Hugo and this website is a big work in progress, so expect updates over the next few weeks. I plan to add Projects and Blog pages to document both professional and personal experiences.
